    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You can spin and juggle a small firearm, making it difficult to predict where you will shoot.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Amateur Gunslinger feat or grit class feature, Dazzling Display, Weapon Focus.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You can spend 1 grit point to make a feint attempt using a one-handed firearm for which you have Weapon Focus (instead of a melee weapon). The target of this feint must be within 30 feet of you and be able to see you.<br/><br/> If you have the Quick Draw feat, you can holster a onehanded firearm as a free action as long as you have at least 1 grit point.",
